When Token Cost is Enabled
By default, LiteLLM returns token usage in all completion requests and exposes three public helper functions: token_counter, cost_per_token, and completion_cost LiteLLM. So cost tracking is enabled by default — you don't need to opt in.
How Token Cost is Computed
